\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\fs32 The Purpose; \ulnone\b0 The cab booking website is a new generation digitalized way of booking cabs. This website/app should be able to satisfy the needs of both customers, as well as drivers. This website also acts as a communication place between cab owners and customers.\ul\par
{\pntext\f0 II.\tab}\b The Targeted Audience; \ulnone\b0 This website mainly targets cab users and employees who are cab owners.\ul\par
{\pntext\f0 III.\tab}\b Scope of the Product; \ulnone\b0 Through this website, customers can book a cab of their choice, select their pickup point, and destination and also pay money whereas the cab drivers can receive an alert and know all the details regarding the booking.\ul\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b\fs36 USER NEEDS\b0\fs32\par
\ulnone There are many existing Cab booking management websites/apps, but the company we are developing the app for is a growing company who are starting to digitalize its existing system. So the product to be developed should have all features in the conventional cab booking websites and should also incorporate new features like driver ratings, premium ratings, etc.\par
\par
\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qc\ul\b\fs36 SOFTWARE REQUIREMENT SPECIFICATION FOR CAB BOOKING\par
\par
