\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\ulnone\b0\fs32 On the opening page the website should show three options:\par
1. User-the person who tries to book the cab\par
2. Driver-the person with a car who is willing to drive the user\par
3. Admin-the one who has control of the product or service\par
After selecting a particular option the website/app will take the user to the specified page.\par
